27-March-1992 - Modules TRIANG, TRIEDIT
.list
.LE;^*TRIANG,TRIEDIT\*#-#These programs have been linked with the new FRTLIB
to prevent warning messages being generated when they are given an FRT file
containing the new 'PRIO' priority entries. See the new FRTLIB user guide
